    "after_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "躺、躺平了……真个躺平了！先生！你这手段，比城里头请的先生还要硬扎！（往他手里头塞钱，塞得嘿实在）",
      "next": "after_2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "laugh"
      }
    },
    "after_2": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 50
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "after_3"
    },
    "after_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "管事只给一回钱，但谢能谢八遍。第三遍起，关二狗已经在想别的事了——刚才那一下，到底是哪样压住的？",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "mid_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（贴着门框，半个身子杵在门外头）先、先生你接到来！小的在这点……在这点给你守起门！",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "就、就是它们两个……老爷子是寄停在这点的，等吉日下葬；外乡那具是船运来的，等屋头人来认领。昨晚上都还好生生躺起的！",
      "next": "n2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "你要使啥子物件，供桌上头都有——米、墨斗、剪子，石头子外头地上多得很。小的就不上前了！",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "jiaoshi_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "管事掀开苇席角，从头到脚扫了一遍，又扫了一遍。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_2"
    },
    "jiaoshi_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "泡了两日往上，水腥都闷出来了。……手脚倒稳当，没蹭没磕，油布包也没人动过。要得。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_put",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "jiaoshi_put": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_管事义庄内",
            "signal": "beishi_yan_delivered"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 8
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "grantRuleLayer",
          "params": {
            "ruleId": "rule_drowned_corpse",
            "layer": "xiang"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "jiaoshi_3"
    },
    "jiaoshi_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "八枚铜钱拍在掌心，一枚不少。管事数钱的手比说话麻利得多。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_4"
    },
    "jiaoshi_4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "记到：淹死的水汽阴沉，上肩就往水那头坠。背起走道，一莫沿水边，二莫蹚积水——街心那摊子雨水塘塘，你蹚没蹚，你脚杆自家晓得。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_end",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "jiaoshi_end": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "keeper_daily": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "义庄重地，生人莫乱走。有正事说正事，没得事就出切。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_end",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "jiaoshi_point": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "淹的嗦？莫往我跟前杵！那边空凳上切——轻些放，脚朝门，头朝里，莫放反了。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_end",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "js_check": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "淹尸_动了死人的东西",
              "op": "==",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "jz_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "jiaoshi_1"
    },
    "jz_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（掀开苇席角，目光在腰上停了一停）……腰杆上咋个有圈新勒痕喃？油布缠的印子还在，包倒莫得了。",
      "next": "jz_2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "jz_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "钱，八文，少不得你的——我不是官面，不管这些。门道嘛，本想顺嘴点你两句……你这号手脚，自家悟切。",
      "next": "jz_put",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "jz_put": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_管事义庄内",
            "signal": "beishi_yan_delivered"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 8
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "jz_3"
    },
    "jz_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "八文到手。管事没再多说一个字，转身去拾掇苇席——那点没说出口的门道，比四文私钱值钱得多。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_end"
    },
    "lg_point": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "拉来的嗦？莫杵到门口——那边空凳上切。轻些放，脚朝门，头朝里，莫放反了。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_end",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "lg_settle_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（掀开苇席角扫了一眼）路倒的？眉眼周正，没伤没破，走得干净。要得。",
      "next": "lg_settle_2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "lg_settle_2": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_管事义庄内",
            "signal": "beishi_lg_delivered"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "giveCurrency",
          "params": {
            "amount": 5
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "lg_settle_3"
    },
    "lg_settle_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "五文，拿好。手脚利索，改日有活还寻你。——记到：背死人子，稳当比快当值钱。",
      "next": "jiaoshi_end",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    }
  }
}
